title: Downplay Discography
description:
Downplay is an American rock band formed in Athens, Ohio in 2002 and now based in Columbus, Ohio. The band consists of Dustin Bates, Ron DeChant and Brian Patrick. The band has released four albums to date and is recording their major label debut with producer Dave Fortman.


Info:

Basically these are ripped from Spotify @ 320 Kbps...

These are not perfect, there is the occasional glitch, but I did the best I can because I couldn't believe nobody was sharing these guys and they are excellent! If you are a purist, go buy the original :-)
in the meantime, please share!

Included Are:

2005: Saturday
2007: A Day without Gravity
2009: Rise, Fall, Repeat.
2011: Beyond the Machine
2012: Radiocalypse
2012: The Human Condition
2013: Stripped
